ruby is a feature film , released in the united states on march 27 , 1992 , about jack ruby , the dallas , texas nightclub owner who shot and killed lee harvey oswald in the basement garage of a dallas city police station in 1963 . the film was directed by john mackenzie and stars danny aiello ( as ruby ) , sherilyn fenn ( as sheryl ann &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; a.k.a. candy cane ) , and arliss howard . it is based on a play written by british screenwriter stephen davis . ruby was released three months after oliver stone 's movie jfk .